{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896/comments/9899832.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896/_/diff#comment-9899832"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1896, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896"}}, "title": "Removing deprecations part 1"}, "content": {"raw": "These functions were deprecated in gazebo6 and are being removed for gazebo7. Users will see these warnings as long as they compile their code against gazebo6 before gazebo7.\n\nDevil's advocate:\n\nThere are ROS indigo users still on gazebo2 or ROS jade users on gazebo5, and their code could break on gazebo7 if it used any of the removed functions. Also any code that wants to compile against gazebo5 and gazebo7 will require ifdef's.\n\nThese aren't necessarily deal-breakers; I'm just trying to think about the consequences. Perhaps we should be explicit about how many major releases will occur between deprecation and removal?", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>These functions were deprecated in gazebo6 and are being removed for gazebo7. Users will see these warnings as long as they compile their code against gazebo6 before gazebo7.</p>\n<p>Devil's advocate:</p>\n<p>There are ROS indigo users still on gazebo2 or ROS jade users on gazebo5, and their code could break on gazebo7 if it used any of the removed functions. Also any code that wants to compile against gazebo5 and gazebo7 will require ifdef's.</p>\n<p>These aren't necessarily deal-breakers; I'm just trying to think about the consequences. Perhaps we should be explicit about how many major releases will occur between deprecation and removal?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-09-14T21:16:29.398395+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Steve Peters", "uuid": "{2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B2ccfed09-18b8-4921-8d58-15ef01092802%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1fb4816dad9e68337d3096f750951f6cd=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsSP-1.png"}}, "nickname": "Steven Peters", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:5de38267-b118-494c-aa76-4fab35448816"}, "updated_on": "2015-09-14T21:16:29.413431+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 9899832}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896/comments/9900927.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896/_/diff#comment-9900927"}}, "parent": {"id": 9899832, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896/comments/9899832.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896/_/diff#comment-9899832"}}, "depth": 1}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1896, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896"}}, "title": "Removing deprecations part 1"}, "content": {"raw": "+1 for being explicit. It would also be nice to explicitly mention every removed function in the migration guide so people can search for them.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>+1 for being explicit. It would also be nice to explicitly mention every removed function in the migration guide so people can search for them.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-09-14T22:01:33.667481+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": "2015-09-14T22:01:33.674957+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 9900927}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896/comments/9901681.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896/_/diff#comment-9901681"}}, "parent": {"id": 9900927, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896/comments/9900927.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896/_/diff#comment-9900927"}}, "depth": 2}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 1896, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/1896.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/1896"}}, "title": "Removing deprecations part 1"}, "content": {"raw": "If the functions are included in the migration guide as deprecated, then we don't need to also add that they have been removed.\n\nI see that many of these deprecated functions were not listed in the migration guide. I'll make that change, and a note to the top of the migration guide about deprecated code.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>If the functions are included in the migration guide as deprecated, then we don't need to also add that they have been removed.</p>\n<p>I see that many of these deprecated functions were not listed in the migration guide. I'll make that change, and a note to the top of the migration guide about deprecated code.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2015-09-14T22:47:18.119242+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Nate Koenig", "uuid": "{c862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Bc862cdd9-fcc8-4419-9fc7-e20db14b8fcb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https:/